## Monorepo (Turborepo)

- **Run tasks from root** — always use `turbo run build`, `turbo run test`, etc. from the repo root
- Shared packages in `packages/` directory — reference via workspace protocol (`"@repo/ui": "workspace:*"`)
- `turbo.json`: define task dependencies correctly (`dependsOn: ["^build"]` for proper build order)
- Never publish `packages/` to npm unless explicitly intended
- Environment variables: use `.env.local` per app, never commit `.env` files
- Cache: Turborepo remote cache speeds up CI — configure with Vercel or self-hosted
- `package.json` scripts: always delegate to `turbo run <task>`
